WEBVTT

00:21.184 --> 00:22.464
笙ｪThat day笙ｪ

00:22.880 --> 00:24.448
笙ｪNothing stays together forever笙ｪ

00:24.448 --> 00:25.792
笙ｪI've quit romance笙ｪ

00:26.218 --> 00:27.920
笙ｪWho hasn't failed again笙ｪ

00:27.920 --> 00:31.424
笙ｪCrying in death笙ｪ

00:31.424 --> 00:34.016
笙ｪAnd in life笙ｪ

00:34.432 --> 00:36.370
笙ｪEven now笙ｪ

00:36.672 --> 00:38.656
笙ｪWe keep learning笙ｪ

00:38.656 --> 00:39.680
笙ｪIt's no surprise笙ｪ

00:39.744 --> 00:42.144
笙ｪBeing happy is so hard笙ｪ

00:42.144 --> 00:43.968
笙ｪWeirdly, I became a role model笙ｪ

00:44.736 --> 00:46.688
笙ｪOn the day we met again, we said hi笙ｪ

00:46.688 --> 00:52.896
笙ｪIt was a reminder,
a test, and a complaint笙ｪ

00:52.896 --> 00:56.003
笙ｪWho can do anything without regret笙ｪ

00:56.003 --> 00:59.424
笙ｪI am all right笙ｪ

01:00.480 --> 01:05.074
笙ｪMay you live in peace笙ｪ

01:05.074 --> 01:07.456
笙ｪLet the world roar笙ｪ

01:07.456 --> 01:09.732
笙ｪSounds like a carnival笙ｪ

01:09.732 --> 01:14.453
笙ｪBeing alive is never dull笙ｪ

01:14.453 --> 01:18.830
笙ｪHow wonderful to be free笙ｪ

01:18.830 --> 01:23.485
笙ｪI became even better without you笙ｪ

01:23.485 --> 01:25.824
笙ｪNothing can be perfect笙ｪ

01:25.824 --> 01:28.224
笙ｪWe bless each other in pain笙ｪ

01:28.224 --> 01:34.234
笙ｪWe nod and smile笙ｪ

01:35.328 --> 01:36.288
笙ｪMay we both be well笙ｪ

01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.066 --> 01:43.727
=Episode 8=

01:44.682 --> 01:48.826
笙ｪI just wanna take my time tonight笙ｪ

01:50.474 --> 01:56.912
笙ｪI go surfing, go diving, go driving,
and go flying to a different place笙ｪ

01:56.912 --> 01:59.568
笙ｪI go drink, go party, and go dance笙ｪ

01:59.568 --> 02:02.378
笙ｪEven if I'm lonely笙ｪ

02:02.378 --> 02:02.979
Madam Yu.

02:04.499 --> 02:05.059
Madam Yu.

02:06.059 --> 02:07.898
I brought a cake for you.

02:09.219 --> 02:10.299
Who are you?

02:11.299 --> 02:12.619
My name is Xu Yan.

02:19.619 --> 02:21.858
I brought you
a delicious osmanthus cake.

02:23.019 --> 02:23.619
Madam Yu.

02:24.698 --> 02:27.059
The cake I made is an osmanthus cake.

02:27.459 --> 02:30.299
It includes the osmanthus jam
my grandma made.

02:30.698 --> 02:31.858
And my grandma said

02:32.299 --> 02:33.739
that having sweets occasionally

02:33.779 --> 02:35.299
makes people happy.

02:36.019 --> 02:38.019
But don't worry. It's not too sweet.

02:46.698 --> 02:47.538
Wipe your hands?

02:49.619 --> 02:52.019
Madam Yu, guess what?

02:52.538 --> 02:53.578
You and my grandma

02:54.098 --> 02:56.779
were born in the same year,
the Year of the Ox.

03:02.378 --> 03:04.219
Coincidentally,
your experiences are similar.

03:04.459 --> 03:08.019
You both contributed
to the borderland construction

03:08.378 --> 03:12.418
and were among the first people
to support Xinjiang. What a coincidence!

03:15.378 --> 03:16.378
We were

03:17.619 --> 03:21.098
born in new China
and grew up under the national flag.

03:22.098 --> 03:24.499
We devoted our lives
to the country's modernization.

03:24.939 --> 03:25.378
Right,

03:27.258 --> 03:29.138
the country's modernization.

03:29.578 --> 03:30.418
That's impressive.

03:31.138 --> 03:31.899
Alright.

03:34.059 --> 03:36.658
Madam Yu, try the osmanthus cake.

03:47.698 --> 03:48.418
Want to taste it?

03:52.258 --> 03:54.858
Who are you?
How did you get into my room?

03:57.538 --> 03:58.939
My name is Xu Yan.

03:59.418 --> 04:00.658
I'm here to see you.

04:00.939 --> 04:02.378
I brought an osmanthus cake.

04:02.459 --> 04:04.098
- You're a thief.
- I'm not a thief.

04:04.098 --> 04:04.899
You're stealing.

04:04.899 --> 04:05.939
Madam Yu, I'm not a thief.

04:05.978 --> 04:07.019
Listen to me, Madam Yu.

04:07.098 --> 04:09.698
- You want to steal vegetable balls.
- I got you vegetable balls.

04:09.779 --> 04:11.899
Madam Yu, I brought vegetable balls.

04:12.538 --> 04:14.098
Your daughter's favorite food.

04:15.059 --> 04:19.458
Vegetable balls? My vegetable balls.

04:27.499 --> 04:30.539
One, two, three, four,

04:30.739 --> 04:35.778
five, six, seven, eight, nine, ten.

04:38.299 --> 04:39.659
Right amount.

04:40.739 --> 04:41.619
All here.

04:55.458 --> 04:56.258
Vegetable balls.

04:57.458 --> 04:58.179
It's warm.

05:03.698 --> 05:04.378
Want to try it?

05:05.299 --> 05:14.179
See if it tastes
like those you make. Taste it.

05:18.739 --> 05:19.859
Vegetable balls.

05:21.659 --> 05:24.338
My daughter's favorite vegetable balls.

05:26.539 --> 05:29.539
My daughter loves vegetable balls.

05:45.059 --> 05:46.499
You...

05:47.698 --> 05:50.739
What happened

05:50.979 --> 05:51.659
to you?

05:55.258 --> 05:56.939
I did it by accident.

05:59.179 --> 06:00.179
It's because

06:00.739 --> 06:02.778
the osmanthus cake is very delicious.

06:03.258 --> 06:03.778
Really.

06:04.499 --> 06:06.378
It smells so good.

06:07.338 --> 06:08.059
Have a taste.

06:15.619 --> 06:17.338
Try a bite.

06:24.778 --> 06:25.578
Is it tasty?

06:28.499 --> 06:30.099
- It's tasty.
- Tasty.

06:36.378 --> 06:37.299
Who are you?

06:40.338 --> 06:41.179
Xu Yan.

06:46.378 --> 06:47.539
If you like,

06:49.539 --> 06:51.218
I can often bring you vegetable balls.

06:57.258 --> 06:57.778
Okay.

06:58.378 --> 07:01.218
Have another bite.
It contains osmanthus jam.

07:05.739 --> 07:06.458
It's tasty.

07:08.018 --> 07:09.258
- It's tasty.
- It's tasty.

07:13.610 --> 07:17.040
(Family Feast)

07:22.698 --> 07:23.619
Have some fruit.

07:25.739 --> 07:26.419
Madam Yu.

07:27.138 --> 07:29.619
Do you want to see what
I'll look like when I turn 70?

07:30.499 --> 07:32.619
Turn 70? I can't believe it.

07:35.018 --> 07:36.299
Look here.

07:36.391 --> 07:38.859
(See what you look like
when you're old.)

07:38.859 --> 07:40.018
Two old ladies.

07:41.619 --> 07:42.939
Now you have a bestie, don't you?

07:49.979 --> 07:54.898
One, two, three, four.

07:56.619 --> 07:57.099
Madam Yu.

07:57.258 --> 07:58.739
Here comes another one. Here.

07:58.739 --> 07:59.138
Okay.

07:59.659 --> 08:00.338
Be careful.

08:00.698 --> 08:01.338
I can help.

08:01.338 --> 08:02.299
Here.

08:03.138 --> 08:03.659
I can help.

08:03.659 --> 08:04.898
Hit.

08:04.898 --> 08:06.378
One less. One less.

08:06.378 --> 08:06.979
Here we go.

08:08.400 --> 08:10.325
笙ｪEven now笙ｪ

08:10.574 --> 08:12.807
笙ｪWe keep learning笙ｪ

08:15.979 --> 08:17.248
- Take your medicine.
- No.

08:17.248 --> 08:18.898
- You must take it.
- I won't.

08:19.594 --> 08:22.270
笙ｪMay you live in peace笙ｪ

08:22.338 --> 08:22.818
Two.

08:24.179 --> 08:24.979
Like this.

08:25.419 --> 08:26.299
Good, three.

08:27.018 --> 08:28.698
Four, five.

08:29.619 --> 08:31.059
Turn around, six.

08:32.858 --> 08:33.578
Here.

08:33.578 --> 08:34.218
Here we go.

08:34.338 --> 08:35.098
Here.

08:37.994 --> 08:42.410
笙ｪI became even better without you笙ｪ

08:42.480 --> 08:45.072
笙ｪNothing can be perfect笙ｪ

08:45.072 --> 08:47.696
笙ｪWe bless each other in pain笙ｪ

08:47.696 --> 08:53.616
笙ｪWe nod and smile笙ｪ

08:54.096 --> 08:55.344
笙ｪOvercome笙ｪ

08:55.344 --> 08:58.228
笙ｪThe obstacles and love ourselves笙ｪ

08:58.986 --> 09:00.080
笙ｪBe so good笙ｪ

09:00.080 --> 09:02.593
笙ｪThat you can't recognize me笙ｪ

09:02.800 --> 09:04.693
笙ｪWhen I can look up笙ｪ

09:05.040 --> 09:07.411
笙ｪAt different clouds笙ｪ

09:08.176 --> 09:12.241
笙ｪI'll embrace the memories笙ｪ

09:12.784 --> 09:16.454
笙ｪIt's good to forget everything笙ｪ

09:17.098 --> 09:18.139
Very good.

09:20.539 --> 09:21.098
Go to sleep.

09:22.442 --> 09:24.857
笙ｪA carefree smile笙ｪ

09:25.106 --> 09:27.152
笙ｪThe heart beats for itself笙ｪ

09:27.248 --> 09:31.792
笙ｪHappy to see each other carefree笙ｪ

09:32.682 --> 09:40.054
笙ｪMay we both be well笙ｪ

10:27.379 --> 10:28.179
Feels good, right?

10:30.299 --> 10:32.218
I wash my grandma's hair like this.

10:32.498 --> 10:34.338
She falls asleep
every time I wash her hair.

10:48.338 --> 10:49.899
Actually, I really want

10:49.939 --> 10:51.618
to bring my grandma to Jingzhou.

10:53.978 --> 10:55.098
But she doesn't want to.

10:57.779 --> 10:58.618
She says it's far.

11:01.059 --> 11:03.218
She's not used to living here
without friends.

11:06.218 --> 11:07.299
Actually, I know

11:08.818 --> 11:09.779
you two are the same,

11:11.139 --> 11:12.539
afraid of troubling your children.

11:20.338 --> 11:21.659
Since that's the case,

11:22.299 --> 11:23.259
what should you do?

11:24.218 --> 11:27.259
Eat well every day
and take your medicine on time.

11:28.139 --> 11:31.498
When the weather is nice,
go out, take a walk and do exercise.

11:31.858 --> 11:33.539
Keep your body healthy and strong.

11:34.338 --> 11:34.858
This way,

11:34.858 --> 11:36.659
we can be together for a long time.

11:40.698 --> 11:41.578
Feels good, right?

11:43.858 --> 11:44.738
Done.

11:46.779 --> 11:47.338
Okay.

12:03.899 --> 12:06.858
I'll wash my hands first
and then help you wash your hair.

12:07.698 --> 12:08.259
Wait a moment.

12:17.698 --> 12:19.218
Let's go.

12:20.218 --> 12:22.419
One, two, three.

12:23.539 --> 12:23.939
Let's go.

12:26.259 --> 12:27.698
Why are you so late?

12:29.179 --> 12:30.019
It took a while.

12:30.419 --> 12:32.379
I'll be quicker next time.
Let me wash your hair.

12:33.698 --> 12:34.978
You lost weight.

12:36.939 --> 12:39.218
Are you too tired?

12:40.059 --> 12:40.779
No.

12:42.139 --> 12:43.179
It's all my fault.

12:43.578 --> 12:45.338
I troubled you, my dear daughter.

12:47.698 --> 12:48.779
Come here.

13:08.498 --> 13:09.818
I made this for you.

13:10.299 --> 13:12.299
Your favorite vegetable balls.

13:16.019 --> 13:17.978
Remember to take them with you later.

13:23.779 --> 13:27.698
Remember to heat them up before eating.

13:28.419 --> 13:31.098
It's not good for your stomach
to eat cold food.

13:37.059 --> 13:38.618
Take good care of yourself.

13:40.139 --> 13:41.578
Then I'll be at ease.

13:50.458 --> 13:51.539
I know.

13:53.698 --> 13:54.779
I know.

13:55.738 --> 13:57.539
I'll heat them up before I eat.

13:58.659 --> 13:59.498
Don't worry.

14:00.779 --> 14:01.338
Mom.

14:27.618 --> 14:29.899
Six, seven, open your arms.

14:30.179 --> 14:31.899
Eight, good.

14:32.659 --> 14:33.218
Two.

14:35.299 --> 14:35.779
Two.

14:36.419 --> 14:40.299
Miss Xu has been here for over a week.
She keeps Madam Yu company every day.

14:40.779 --> 14:41.299
Seven.

14:42.698 --> 14:43.259
Eight.

14:44.019 --> 14:45.419
Relax.

14:48.139 --> 14:48.899
Feels good, right?

14:49.419 --> 14:50.458
That's it for today.

14:50.618 --> 14:51.939
Let's have breakfast.

14:51.939 --> 14:53.139
Okay, Xu Yan.

14:57.899 --> 14:59.019
What did you just call me?

15:00.578 --> 15:01.698
I called you Xu Yan.

15:03.338 --> 15:04.818
You remember my name?

15:05.618 --> 15:07.539
I've always remembered your name.

15:07.698 --> 15:09.779
You've always remembered my name?

15:09.978 --> 15:11.659
What else do you remember?

15:12.259 --> 15:14.299
I also remember

15:14.338 --> 15:15.498
the delicious osmanthus cake.

15:15.498 --> 15:16.139
Cake.

15:16.498 --> 15:17.858
You helped me catch the thief.

15:17.899 --> 15:18.578
Catch the thief.

15:18.818 --> 15:20.659
And you took photos with me.

15:22.379 --> 15:24.458
You're so great! Let me hug you.

15:25.179 --> 15:25.738
Come on.

15:26.059 --> 15:26.779
You can't.

15:26.779 --> 15:27.379
One more hug.

15:27.698 --> 15:28.738
Be careful. Don't move.

15:48.858 --> 15:51.539
Mr. Shen, you're a winner in life.

15:53.019 --> 15:55.259
You're great at golf
and have a successful career.

15:55.539 --> 15:57.738
And you married a good wife,

15:58.098 --> 15:59.659
who's been helping you all along.

16:00.059 --> 16:00.578
Helping me?

16:01.698 --> 16:03.698
Mr. Huang, I don't quite understand.

16:04.338 --> 16:07.698
Wasn't it you who asked your wife
to take care of my mother-in-law?

16:08.978 --> 16:09.899
Recently,

16:10.059 --> 16:12.578
Xu Yan has been
taking care of my mother-in-law.

16:13.098 --> 16:15.498
My mother-in-law's condition
has improved.

16:15.779 --> 16:17.779
Her state is much better than before.

16:19.059 --> 16:20.858
Didn't you know?

16:22.299 --> 16:23.299
She never told me.

16:26.858 --> 16:28.738
Maybe it's just a coincidence.

16:29.139 --> 16:29.818
Anyway,

16:30.059 --> 16:32.738
please be sure to convey my gratitude
to your wife.

16:33.019 --> 16:33.978
Sure, no problem.

16:34.419 --> 16:36.578
But I invited you today

16:37.259 --> 16:39.059
just to thank your wife.

16:39.379 --> 16:42.698
So today we're just playing golf,
without talking about the work.

16:44.818 --> 16:47.818
Actually, you take the time
to play golf with me,

16:48.019 --> 16:49.098
which is already my honor.

16:50.098 --> 16:51.098
After all, you must be

16:51.139 --> 16:53.059
stressed about your group's issues.

16:53.458 --> 16:55.978
It's good to come out
and play golf to relax.

16:57.539 --> 16:58.779
I'm not stressed at all.

17:00.098 --> 17:01.458
Shouke is well-funded,

17:02.578 --> 17:04.899
but its structure isn't mature enough.

17:06.139 --> 17:09.018
It is lacking professional talent
and human resources.

17:09.939 --> 17:11.819
Even if you acquire Plot 178,

17:12.179 --> 17:13.498
you can't develop it.

17:13.819 --> 17:15.659
Isn't that something
you should worry about?

17:16.538 --> 17:17.819
Young man,

17:18.139 --> 17:19.379
you're quite bold.

17:20.579 --> 17:21.579
Understaffing and staying

17:22.018 --> 17:23.099
outside the core circle

17:23.099 --> 17:24.698
of the real estate industry.

17:25.619 --> 17:27.498
These two have been Shouke's concerns

17:27.698 --> 17:29.018
and stumbling blocks.

17:30.179 --> 17:32.458
You want to tackle these issues, right?

17:33.939 --> 17:35.139
So, Mr. Shen,

17:36.058 --> 17:38.379
do you have any suggestions?

17:39.139 --> 17:42.018
Shifeng and Mingyuan Group

17:43.939 --> 17:45.058
are currently

17:45.179 --> 17:47.218
in a fierce contention.

17:48.819 --> 17:50.139
If Shouke now

17:50.659 --> 17:52.018
works with Shifeng,

17:53.058 --> 17:54.859
it will be a win-win cooperation.

17:55.659 --> 17:57.258
Mingyuan is bound to lose.

17:58.778 --> 18:00.218
Shouke has the land

18:00.738 --> 18:02.298
and can use Shifeng

18:03.018 --> 18:04.778
to upgrade its entire structure.

18:05.659 --> 18:08.458
In the future,
your company is sure to stand out.

18:09.139 --> 18:11.139
It will secure entry to the core circle.

18:14.939 --> 18:16.899
Let's have a meal together
after the game,

18:17.099 --> 18:17.939
and we'll discuss it.

18:27.379 --> 18:29.778
That's ridiculous.
Isn't she afraid of being found out?

18:29.819 --> 18:30.379
Yeah.

18:31.859 --> 18:33.899
- What are you looking at?
- Siwei.

18:34.339 --> 18:36.339
Look at this news. We're all shocked.

18:36.778 --> 18:39.939
There's an incredible woman
hiding her true family background.

18:39.939 --> 18:42.018
(A Wedding Scam behind Large Dowries)
She held weddings with three men

18:42.218 --> 18:44.659
and obtained huge dowries
and properties from them.

18:44.738 --> 18:47.379
Moreover, more than 100 guests
attending the wedding invited by her

18:47.419 --> 18:48.819
were all hired actors.

18:49.058 --> 18:50.458
Luckily, the truth came out,

18:50.698 --> 18:52.099
and the groom called the police.

18:53.179 --> 18:54.778
That's outrageous. Let me see.

18:56.058 --> 18:57.099
That's ridiculous.

18:57.419 --> 18:59.099
She isn't afraid of being found out.

18:59.179 --> 19:00.579
Yeah.

19:00.819 --> 19:02.139
It's so dramatic.

19:02.379 --> 19:03.218
Right.

19:04.298 --> 19:04.738
Stop.

19:06.218 --> 19:07.099
What's wrong?

19:09.339 --> 19:10.498
Nothing.

19:11.419 --> 19:12.619
This person

19:14.498 --> 19:16.258
looks so familiar.

19:16.538 --> 19:17.978
- Familiar? Who is it?
- Who is it?

19:18.379 --> 19:19.978
When she first came here,

19:20.058 --> 19:23.899
I clearly remember
that she said she only had a grandma.

19:24.939 --> 19:28.419
When does she have intellectual parents
who live abroad?

19:30.458 --> 19:32.258
- Send me this link.
- Okay.

19:35.058 --> 19:36.179
- Sir.
- Come in.

19:38.018 --> 19:38.579
Sir.

19:39.258 --> 19:41.819
An interview guest gave me a box of tea.

19:42.139 --> 19:43.139
It looked pretty nice.

19:43.179 --> 19:45.218
I haven't had it yet.
I brought it for you.

19:45.659 --> 19:46.179
What's up?

19:47.899 --> 19:50.139
Look how observant you are!

19:50.538 --> 19:50.978
Go ahead.

19:52.218 --> 19:53.058
Earlier,

19:53.619 --> 19:56.099
- you went to Xu Yan's wedding, right?
- Yes, I did.

19:56.379 --> 19:58.859
Did you take photos then?
Could you show them to me?

20:01.379 --> 20:01.978
Why?

20:02.819 --> 20:05.258
A friend of mine is getting married
next month.

20:05.819 --> 20:07.659
I'd like to watch a high-society wedding

20:07.738 --> 20:09.298
to see how they set it up.

20:09.619 --> 20:10.179
Well,

20:12.258 --> 20:13.339
I did take some photos,

20:13.698 --> 20:16.099
but they were very strict
about this matter.

20:16.379 --> 20:19.018
Taking photos and sharing
on social media weren't allowed.

20:19.819 --> 20:21.458
I just snuck a few shots.

20:22.498 --> 20:24.579
Why don't you ask Xu Yan for them?

20:24.778 --> 20:26.698
Sir, you know very well

20:26.738 --> 20:28.339
I'm not on good terms with Xu Yan.

20:34.179 --> 20:35.258
Alright then.

20:36.058 --> 20:37.018
You watch photos here.

20:37.738 --> 20:39.698
Don't worry. I won't tell anyone.

20:41.139 --> 20:42.579
- Thanks.
- You watch right here.

20:42.899 --> 20:43.458
Okay.

20:43.498 --> 20:44.899
I'll taste your tea leaves.

20:53.659 --> 20:56.058
The high-society wedding
is indeed different.

20:56.339 --> 20:57.619
That cost a lot of money.

20:59.139 --> 21:00.698
But a wealthy family can afford it.

21:00.978 --> 21:02.538
It's really nice.

21:03.579 --> 21:05.018
Speaking of their wedding,

21:05.538 --> 21:07.018
it's truly enviable.

21:07.738 --> 21:09.058
It's high-end and impressive.

21:09.939 --> 21:12.698
I have to take a good look
for reference.

21:13.018 --> 21:15.759
I'm telling you, learn a thing or two.

21:15.759 --> 21:17.859
When you get married,
you hold a better wedding.

21:17.859 --> 21:18.498
Sure.

21:19.419 --> 21:21.778
Sir, you got the beauty filter on!

21:22.939 --> 21:24.458
To reduce wrinkles on my face.

21:25.538 --> 21:26.778
Alright, I'm done.

21:26.899 --> 21:27.899
Well, I have to go.

21:27.939 --> 21:31.018
- Okay.
- When you run out, I'll get you more.

21:31.058 --> 21:32.619
Alright, this smells nice.

22:07.819 --> 22:09.258
Look, it's right here.

22:09.859 --> 22:10.859
No. 16 Yunshui Street.

22:11.698 --> 22:13.698
Are you sure?
We've gone around several times.

22:14.058 --> 22:14.778
I'm sure.

22:15.339 --> 22:18.698
I've been a paparazzo for three years.
Finding people is my specialty.

22:21.738 --> 22:22.978
Look, isn't that him?

22:24.458 --> 22:26.179
Look, it's him, right?

22:27.778 --> 22:28.619
Xu Yan's father.

22:33.659 --> 22:34.218
Hello.

22:40.218 --> 22:41.058
Miss,

22:41.579 --> 22:43.819
I really don't understand
what you're saying.

22:44.579 --> 22:46.379
I think you've mistaken me
for someone else.

22:47.058 --> 22:48.498
Don't believe me? Check my ID.

22:50.379 --> 22:50.859
Here.

22:52.258 --> 22:54.298
My surname isn't Xu. It's Gao.

22:55.018 --> 22:56.058
Gao Liangjie,

22:56.179 --> 22:57.538
meaning unwavering integrity.

22:57.698 --> 22:58.819
Don't panic.

22:59.339 --> 23:00.899
You don't need to admit anything now.

23:01.458 --> 23:02.778
Since we could find you,

23:02.859 --> 23:04.498
it definitely wasn't without reason.

23:05.218 --> 23:06.058
Let's cooperate.

23:20.298 --> 23:20.939
Xu Yan.

23:25.899 --> 23:27.819
The finance department needs a host.

23:28.379 --> 23:31.379
The leadership plans
to select from young hosts.

23:31.698 --> 23:32.659
I heard you signed up.

23:35.139 --> 23:36.139
Are you also interested?

23:37.859 --> 23:38.619
Of course.

23:39.218 --> 23:41.339
Who would miss
such a good opportunity to pivot?

23:45.978 --> 23:48.819
But I don't plan to read the script
they've prepared for me.

23:50.099 --> 23:52.978
I want to use the news
I've personally gathered and edited

23:53.058 --> 23:54.018
to make a demo.

23:58.099 --> 24:00.058
We're drowning in information.

24:00.738 --> 24:02.538
Separating fact from fiction

24:02.619 --> 24:04.498
and giving the public truth,
genuine insight,

24:04.538 --> 24:05.899
and sincere affection

24:06.419 --> 24:07.579
is what truly matters.

24:09.419 --> 24:10.899
I can see you've been working hard.

24:12.058 --> 24:13.538
Your thinking seems beyond you.

24:16.978 --> 24:17.899
Rest assured.

24:18.419 --> 24:21.179
My demo is absolutely genuine

24:21.698 --> 24:23.058
and impactful enough.

24:24.139 --> 24:26.619
It will definitely be unforgettable.

24:30.018 --> 24:30.778
Good luck.

24:31.058 --> 24:31.579
Thank you.

24:50.458 --> 24:52.419
Please begin
reading the assigned script.

24:52.733 --> 24:56.016
(News Program Host Selection Contest)

24:58.778 --> 25:01.498
Recently, a cold wave
named Niuniu Niuniu Six

25:01.538 --> 25:03.379
came from the Scandinavian Peninsula.

25:03.458 --> 25:06.819
It will pass
through Norin-Sebestei-Bvlag,

25:06.939 --> 25:08.899
Barunbagabayanner,

25:09.018 --> 25:11.579
Tuiraomuyin, and Ulantaolegai,
and so on.

25:11.738 --> 25:14.099
Please use simple terms
to tell the audience

25:14.179 --> 25:16.258
about the meanings
of physical settlement,

25:16.298 --> 25:18.899
cash settlement, and leverage
in futures.

25:20.179 --> 25:21.738
You book a bag.

25:22.498 --> 25:23.978
The sales tells you it's arrived.

25:24.099 --> 25:25.978
You buy it and then resell it.

25:26.139 --> 25:30.058
That's called physical settlement.

25:30.058 --> 25:33.458
You find that the spot price
is way higher than the price you booked.

25:33.859 --> 25:36.978
So you plan to sell the booked bag
directly to your peers.

25:37.139 --> 25:40.419
That's called cash settlement.

25:41.179 --> 25:43.339
You decided to use 100 yuan
to buy the bag

25:43.538 --> 25:45.939
and resell it to your peers
to earn a 10 yuan spread.

25:46.139 --> 25:48.419
But in the end,
you only spent 10 yuan on a deposit

25:48.498 --> 25:51.179
and directly sold the bag to your peers,
earning a 10 yuan spread.

25:51.498 --> 25:54.258
That's called leverage.

25:54.859 --> 25:55.538
As a host,

25:55.619 --> 25:58.218
do you think it's more important
to speak logically

25:58.298 --> 25:59.298
or to speak with facts?

26:07.458 --> 26:11.218
News has been defined
as the first draft of history.

26:11.778 --> 26:13.538
So in this draft,

26:14.018 --> 26:14.978
the factual part

26:15.018 --> 26:17.379
can be handled by reporters and others.

26:17.698 --> 26:18.698
But the logical part

26:19.379 --> 26:20.859
is to be elevated by the host.

26:21.139 --> 26:22.419
Everyone saw it, right?

26:22.498 --> 26:23.939
Yan was overwhelming.

26:24.058 --> 26:25.978
She amazed the judges in three rounds.

26:26.258 --> 26:27.339
When Yan hosts,

26:27.339 --> 26:28.778
she's always confident,

26:28.819 --> 26:30.218
poised, and natural.

26:30.419 --> 26:31.579
What's most important?

26:31.978 --> 26:33.419
The audience likes her.

26:34.139 --> 26:36.579
The results aren't out yet.
Let's not say anything.

26:36.939 --> 26:39.698
If you go on, I'll be so embarrassed.

26:39.899 --> 26:42.179
Yan, you'll definitely make it.

26:42.538 --> 26:46.698
- Treat us!
- Treat us!

26:46.778 --> 26:49.659
Alright, tonight's dinner is on me.

26:49.899 --> 26:52.099
Order whatever you like, okay?

26:53.139 --> 26:55.179
- Go back to work.
- Work.

26:55.179 --> 26:55.659
Hurry up.

26:55.698 --> 26:56.379
Back to work.

26:58.339 --> 27:00.899
By the way, Yu, fix the thing
we discussed earlier.

27:02.218 --> 27:02.738
Xu Yan.

27:04.179 --> 27:04.698
Xu Yan.

27:06.218 --> 27:07.099
Here you are.

27:10.099 --> 27:10.698
What's up?

27:13.379 --> 27:14.819
Didn't I tell you

27:15.339 --> 27:16.978
that I want to make a news demo?

27:17.498 --> 27:18.538
It's really unfortunate.

27:18.579 --> 27:20.018
My guest is stuck in traffic.

27:20.058 --> 27:21.258
He needs another hour.

27:21.579 --> 27:22.939
Can you be my guest?

27:23.258 --> 27:24.379
Please, help me out.

27:27.298 --> 27:30.018
Yan, the editing room is waiting
for you to review the footage.

27:35.498 --> 27:38.498
I didn't know about your interview
or have background research.

27:39.139 --> 27:40.778
How can I be your guest?

27:42.058 --> 27:43.899
It's just some simple Q&A.

27:44.058 --> 27:45.099
Plus, it's pre-recorded.

27:45.139 --> 27:46.659
We can stop when there's a mistake.

27:46.738 --> 27:47.419
Right, sir?

27:49.419 --> 27:50.058
Miss Xu.

27:50.698 --> 27:52.579
Miss Sun asked everyone,
and no one is available.

27:53.018 --> 27:53.498
Sir...

27:53.659 --> 27:54.778
I'll go to the editing room.

27:55.659 --> 27:56.339
You help her.

28:02.698 --> 28:03.179
Okay.

28:03.698 --> 28:05.579
Xu Yan, thank you so much.

28:05.619 --> 28:06.778
I'm counting on you fully.

28:14.698 --> 28:16.939
(Talk to Weiwei)
I'm honored to have my great partner,

28:16.978 --> 28:19.899
Ms. Xu Yan, the main planner
of Family Feast,

28:20.058 --> 28:22.419
to discuss
hot social issues with us here.

28:27.778 --> 28:30.018
Recently, I came across a news report.

28:30.218 --> 28:32.698
(A Wedding Scam behind Large Dowries)
A married woman hid her marital history

28:32.778 --> 28:35.619
and hired people to impersonate
family and friends to hold a wedding,

28:35.659 --> 28:38.859
aiming at swindling the man
out of a huge dowry.

28:50.819 --> 28:53.379
Mr. Gao, the extra in this news story,

28:53.379 --> 28:54.419
is also here with us.

28:54.538 --> 28:55.339
Let's welcome him.

28:57.419 --> 28:59.179
(The worst-case scenario just happened.)

28:59.899 --> 29:02.859
(I know I'm standing
on the edge of a cliff right now.)

29:09.058 --> 29:10.738
- Hello, Mr. Gao.
- Hello, Miss Sun.

29:11.698 --> 29:14.258
Miss Xu, what a coincidence
to see you here.

29:16.179 --> 29:17.738
Mr. Gao, do you know Xu Yan?

29:18.339 --> 29:19.419
We know each other well.

29:20.698 --> 29:21.978
Where did you two meet?

29:22.899 --> 29:24.538
I... I don't really remember.

29:25.738 --> 29:26.939
I don't know where.

29:28.218 --> 29:28.778
You...

29:29.579 --> 29:30.339
Look at her.

29:30.738 --> 29:31.339
It's okay.

29:31.538 --> 29:32.538
Let's sit down and talk.

29:32.698 --> 29:33.419
Alright.

29:42.339 --> 29:42.939
Mr. Gao,

29:43.258 --> 29:44.859
may I ask what the reason was

29:44.859 --> 29:47.339
that made you impersonate
a wedding guest?

29:49.778 --> 29:52.619
Actually, many people
sought me out before.

29:52.859 --> 29:56.218
Some did so
because their families lack members.

29:56.659 --> 29:58.379
They wanted me to liven things up.

29:58.698 --> 30:00.899
Others did it purely for appearances.

30:01.258 --> 30:04.379
They were afraid
the event wouldn't measure up

30:04.419 --> 30:05.339
to the in-laws.

30:06.298 --> 30:08.258
Were there any cases
of marriage fraud among them?

30:13.778 --> 30:15.298
Yes, there were.

30:18.419 --> 30:22.419
Mr. Gao, this could be seen as fraud.

30:22.538 --> 30:25.018
Once exposed,
you might face criminal charges.

30:26.458 --> 30:28.099
It was always the bride
committing fraud.

30:28.698 --> 30:30.899
I only found out afterwards.

30:31.139 --> 30:33.258
I really regretted it.

30:33.298 --> 30:34.619
I really did.

30:34.659 --> 30:36.859
I shouldn't have gone along with them.

30:37.619 --> 30:40.579
We can see that Mr. Gao
has reflected deeply.

30:40.659 --> 30:42.538
It's alright.
We learn from our mistakes.

30:43.298 --> 30:45.139
As law-abiding citizens,

30:45.179 --> 30:47.018
- we must follow the law.
- Yes.

30:47.058 --> 30:49.450
- We must not go down the wrong path.
- Yes.

30:54.288 --> 30:56.976
Mr. Gao, the person
in the photo is you, right?

30:57.468 --> 30:58.738
Yes, that's me.

30:59.978 --> 31:02.619
What role did you play at the wedding?

31:03.579 --> 31:04.339
The bride's father.

31:05.018 --> 31:06.458
It's a double fate.

31:06.538 --> 31:07.419
Double fate.

31:20.458 --> 31:21.659
Isn't this Ms. Xu's wedding?

31:21.978 --> 31:23.179
What's going on?

31:23.339 --> 31:24.819
Was he at her wedding ceremony?

31:25.099 --> 31:27.058
I must say, they do look alike.

31:33.619 --> 31:34.298
Mr. Gao,

31:36.058 --> 31:37.018
what about this photo?

31:46.939 --> 31:47.458
Well...

31:47.619 --> 31:48.458
What do you mean?

31:51.018 --> 31:55.819
I discovered by chance
while investigating this news story

31:55.899 --> 32:00.258
that Mr. Gao and Xu Yan's father
might be the same person.

32:00.778 --> 32:03.538
As journalists,
we need to get to the bottom of things

32:03.579 --> 32:04.939
and pursue the truth.

32:05.379 --> 32:06.218
Mr. Gao,

32:06.698 --> 32:09.538
you seem to have known Miss Xu
for a long time.

32:10.179 --> 32:11.738
What's your relationship?

32:11.859 --> 32:14.339
Is the person in the photo actually you?

32:14.379 --> 32:16.859
Are you Xu Yan's fake father?

32:16.859 --> 32:18.099
Please answer directly.

32:18.579 --> 32:19.379
Sun Siwei,

32:21.419 --> 32:22.458
you've gone too far.

32:24.298 --> 32:26.899
I didn't expect you
to be this unreasonable.

32:27.298 --> 32:30.099
Does anyone here not know
that we have a bad relationship?

32:30.659 --> 32:31.819
You've always belittled me.

32:32.458 --> 32:33.458
You coveted my guests,

32:33.579 --> 32:34.498
broadcast slots,

32:34.939 --> 32:35.978
and makeup artists.

32:36.139 --> 32:37.419
I can put up with all of that.

32:38.018 --> 32:38.819
But what's this?

32:39.458 --> 32:40.458
What do you want to do?

32:40.538 --> 32:41.698
You're being ridiculous.

32:41.859 --> 32:43.498
Xu Yan, you're stopping Mr. Gao

32:43.498 --> 32:44.218
from talking.

32:44.218 --> 32:45.498
Are you hiding something?

32:45.819 --> 32:46.419
Mr. Gao,

32:46.978 --> 32:48.698
there are many people
in the studio today.

32:48.738 --> 32:50.819
Everyone present can witness this.

32:50.859 --> 32:53.579
You don't need to be afraid.
No one can do anything to you.

32:54.258 --> 32:56.579
You just need to tell me clearly.

32:56.819 --> 32:59.458
Is the person in the photo you?

32:59.458 --> 33:02.139
Did you pretend to be Xu Yan's father?

33:22.619 --> 33:24.859
No, that person is not me.

33:27.058 --> 33:28.258
He looks a lot like him.

33:30.218 --> 33:31.058
Aren't they the same?

33:31.058 --> 33:32.139
Is he serious?

33:37.339 --> 33:38.978
Look carefully before you speak.

33:39.819 --> 33:40.859
I have looked carefully.

33:41.538 --> 33:43.738
I can't possibly not recognize myself.

33:48.899 --> 33:50.579
This photo is quite clear.

33:50.579 --> 33:52.899
The facial features
are from the same person.

33:53.258 --> 33:55.379
If you say it's not you, tell me,

33:55.379 --> 33:57.258
what were you doing
on September 20th this year?

33:57.258 --> 33:59.018
Did you go to Xu Yan's wedding?

33:59.738 --> 34:01.218
Miss Sun.

34:02.458 --> 34:04.939
I admit that I'm in that photo.

34:05.379 --> 34:07.218
But I'm not in this photo.

34:07.538 --> 34:09.339
If I had such an aura and demeanor,

34:09.379 --> 34:11.018
would I still be doing this job?

34:11.859 --> 34:14.498
Yes, this gentleman
may look a bit like me.

34:14.779 --> 34:17.178
But in this world,
let alone just looking alike,

34:17.299 --> 34:19.299
there are even people
who look exactly the same.

34:19.379 --> 34:21.978
Even their own parents
might not recognize them, right?

34:23.178 --> 34:24.939
How do you explain
knowing each other before?

34:25.018 --> 34:26.178
How did you know each other?

34:27.138 --> 34:29.138
Well, that's a long story.

34:29.339 --> 34:33.819
Once, the Family Feast show
recruited off-site guests.

34:34.219 --> 34:35.178
And I signed up.

34:35.498 --> 34:38.578
It happened to be Miss Xu
who received us.

34:38.739 --> 34:41.219
Let me tell you,
Miss Xu was very enthusiastic.

34:41.458 --> 34:43.058
She looked after our meals every day.

34:43.178 --> 34:45.098
In the evening,
she even helped us go over...

34:45.138 --> 34:45.819
What's it again?

34:45.939 --> 34:47.018
You're talking nonsense!

34:48.138 --> 34:49.658
Stop the machines. Stop the recording.

34:49.978 --> 34:51.379
Has Ms. Sun gone crazy?

34:51.819 --> 34:53.058
This is clearly framing.

34:54.058 --> 34:54.739
Sun Siwei,

34:55.538 --> 34:56.899
I'll show you more evidence.

34:58.058 --> 34:59.299
Huanhuan, give me the phone.

35:02.299 --> 35:05.618
Mr. Gao, you have
a birthmark here, right?

35:05.739 --> 35:06.259
Yes.

35:06.739 --> 35:07.699
I have a birthmark here.

35:07.978 --> 35:09.299
Look, here it is.

35:09.779 --> 35:11.219
Look here.

35:16.178 --> 35:17.379
Put it onto the big screen.

35:17.578 --> 35:18.018
Okay.

35:19.699 --> 35:20.739
I'm sorry about today.

35:20.779 --> 35:21.978
It's alright.

35:23.458 --> 35:24.419
I told the truth.

35:29.578 --> 35:30.538
Is this by script?

35:31.018 --> 35:32.058
I think so.

35:32.458 --> 35:33.498
Is it real or not?

35:36.498 --> 35:38.739
All these materials given need to be...

35:40.939 --> 35:41.538
I'm sorry.

35:42.578 --> 35:44.538
What's this here?

35:46.618 --> 35:48.259
A birthmark.
I've had it since childhood.

35:49.098 --> 35:51.339
It must be covered starting tomorrow.

35:51.819 --> 35:52.458
No problem.

35:52.699 --> 35:53.859
My father has no birthmarks.

35:55.779 --> 35:56.899
Do you believe it now?

36:09.939 --> 36:11.259
You colluded, right?

36:12.339 --> 36:13.739
Setting me up, huh?

36:20.498 --> 36:21.739
I advise you to calm down.

36:39.419 --> 36:40.259
Don't worry.

36:40.379 --> 36:43.138
My demo is absolutely genuine

36:43.259 --> 36:44.458
and impactful enough.

36:44.578 --> 36:47.018
It will definitely be unforgettable.

36:47.859 --> 36:48.578
Good luck.

36:48.859 --> 36:49.458
Thank you.

37:03.339 --> 37:04.018
Where are you?

37:05.498 --> 37:06.098
Let's meet.

37:07.018 --> 37:07.859
I understand.

37:08.178 --> 37:09.739
Miss Xu, please rest assured.

37:10.018 --> 37:11.739
I will never betray you.

37:21.058 --> 37:22.458
What do you mean, Sir?

37:22.498 --> 37:24.498
Why must I take a break for a while?

37:25.339 --> 37:26.578
Pause your work.

37:27.259 --> 37:28.419
Is it clear enough now?

37:29.018 --> 37:31.259
Your demo from last time's evaluation

37:31.899 --> 37:33.058
made such a big fuss.

37:34.458 --> 37:36.578
The most infuriating thing
is that you lied to me.

37:37.178 --> 37:38.138
You stole my photo.

37:39.498 --> 37:40.939
It's lucky you haven't been fired.

37:41.658 --> 37:42.739
Don't push it.

37:43.339 --> 37:45.058
I was tricked too.

37:55.219 --> 37:57.098
Mom, Xu Yan is bullying me a lot.

37:57.219 --> 37:58.219
What happened this time?

37:58.899 --> 37:59.939
She's picking on me.

37:59.939 --> 38:00.859
You have to help me.

38:00.939 --> 38:02.458
How can I help with your work issues?

38:02.739 --> 38:03.578
Handle it yourself.

38:04.138 --> 38:04.899
I don't care.

38:16.699 --> 38:17.379
Sun Siwei,

38:19.379 --> 38:21.138
you're trying too hard to take me down.

38:22.178 --> 38:23.578
When you try too hard,

38:24.699 --> 38:25.899
it becomes ugly.

38:29.178 --> 38:30.739
Don't think because you married well,

38:30.739 --> 38:32.978
you're actually someone important.

38:33.259 --> 38:35.219
You're not fit to shine my shoes.

38:36.739 --> 38:39.058
Your little tricks
that can't be presented

38:39.259 --> 38:41.098
can fool others but not me.

38:41.458 --> 38:43.018
You're just a liar.

39:01.419 --> 39:02.458
Yes, I'm a liar.

39:05.618 --> 39:06.739
Even if I'm a liar,

39:07.219 --> 39:08.219
I still have the ability

39:08.339 --> 39:10.458
to turn you into a dog
begging me for food.

39:20.299 --> 39:20.899
Yan!

39:23.058 --> 39:23.658
Are you okay?

39:29.538 --> 39:30.618
What's with that acting?

39:34.219 --> 39:35.339
Are you Sun Siwei?

39:35.739 --> 39:36.496
I am.

39:44.779 --> 39:46.658
Chen Lin, inform the Legal Department

39:47.339 --> 39:48.779
to drop everything they're doing

39:48.939 --> 39:50.178
and gather in the meeting room.

39:50.339 --> 39:54.458
My wife is bullied at work. Let them
have a plan to hold her accountable.

39:54.658 --> 39:55.498
She's Sun Siwei.

39:59.018 --> 39:59.498
Let's go.

40:13.058 --> 40:14.299
All departments, get ready.

40:14.339 --> 40:15.098
Host, get ready.

40:15.419 --> 40:16.138
Counting down.

40:16.458 --> 40:16.978
Five.

40:17.379 --> 40:17.978
Four.

40:18.339 --> 40:18.899
Three.

40:19.339 --> 40:19.899
Two.

40:20.498 --> 40:21.098
One.

40:21.379 --> 40:23.058
Hello, audience.

40:23.299 --> 40:24.899
(The NASDAQ hits a record high)
Welcome to Financial News.

40:24.899 --> 40:26.098
I'm your host, Xu Yan.

40:26.687 --> 40:28.603
笙ｪLike fireworks that loved笙ｪ

40:28.603 --> 40:30.262
笙ｪRushing toward the stars笙ｪ

40:30.262 --> 40:32.321
笙ｪUndaunted by pain笙ｪ

40:32.870 --> 40:35.065
